We played a few giant shows in Sao Paulo and we hope they made us fit for this concert in Costa Rica.
We really want to play there.
We love this country, we love surfing and we love the jungle, and Costa Rica is one of the best countries in the world.
How did you get to know Costa Rica and its surfing waves?
Many of our friends are surfers and I have a great friend who lives in Tamarindo, where the waves are simply unimaginable.
My friends have always driven to Costa Rica and Nicaragua for surfing. Together with Mexico are the excellent areas for surfing. In this way, we have learned about people who love surfing.
With a look at the tour, you have offered giant shows with many songs.
What are your plans for the event in Costa Rica?
