With this tour, you celebrate your twenty-year history.
When you look back, do you find it hard to believe in your success?
Yes the total.
First of all, I think no one of us ever imagined playing in a great rock band for over 20 years.
We continue to put on this blessing and it’s great to be able to make music together even now.
We love each other and are enthusiastic about creating music.
We are lucky to be able to go to the places in the world that we have always wanted to visit.
Things could not be better.
What did it mean for you to participate actively in the birth of Grunge?
